## Architecture (hexagonal)

```
<% if (Type === 'publisher') { -%>
src/index.ts                                 composition root: creates the <%= Broker %> publisher + graceful stop
config/config.ts                             env-driven config
src/domain/<%= EntityLower %>.ts                          business types (camelCase)
src/adapter/outbound/publisher/publisher.ts  <%= Entity %> event publisher (wraps pubsub.Publisher)
<% } else { -%>
src/index.ts                                 composition root: Elysia/runtime + ALS + middleware + graceful stop
config/config.ts                             env-driven config
src/domain/<%= EntityLower %>.ts                          business types (camelCase)
src/port/<%= EntityLower %>.ts                            <%= Entity %>Repository interface (driven port)
src/port/<%= EntityLower %>-service.ts                    <%= Entity %>Service interface (the use-case contract)
src/service/<%= EntityLower %>.ts                         use-cases — `satisfies <%= Entity %>Service`
<% if (Type === 'api') { -%>
src/service/stub/<%= EntityLower %>.ts                    canned stub (tree-shaken from prod build)
src/service/factory.ts                       SERVICE_BACKEND switch
<% } -%>
src/apperr/<%= EntityLower %>.ts                          error-code registry
<% if (Database !== 'none') { -%>
src/db/schema/<%= EntityLower %>.ts                       Drizzle table
src/adapter/outbound/repository/<%= EntityLower %>.ts     Drizzle repo (BaseRepo/CachedRepo)
<% } -%>
<% if (Type === 'api') { -%>
src/adapter/inbound/http/<%= EntityLower %>.ts            thin Elysia controller (routes)
src/adapter/inbound/http/<%= EntityLower %>.dto.ts        TypeBox DTO + wire<->domain mapping
<% } else { -%>
src/adapter/inbound/subscriber/handler.ts    message handler (decode → service)
<% } -%>
<% } -%>
```

<% if (Type === 'publisher') { -%>
**Dependency rule (DIP):** the publisher adapter depends on the `Publisher` port from
`@peruri/ts-lib/pubsub` — the broker is swappable without touching call sites. Wiring
happens only in `src/index.ts`.
<% } else { -%>
**Dependency rule (DIP):** `service/` imports `port/` only — never a concrete adapter.
The inbound adapter and the repository depend *inward* on the ports; everything is
substitutable (swap the cache for `nop()`, the repo for a fake, in tests).
<% } -%>

## Request → response flow
<% if (Type === 'api') { %>
```
HTTP  GET /api/v1/<%= EntityLower %>s/:id
  │
  ▼  serverPlugin.onRequest         x-request-id (gen/echo) + AsyncLocalStorage(request logger)
  ▼  Elysia route + TypeBox         validates `body` on POST/PUT  ──► fail = onError(VALIDATION) ─► 422
  │
  ▼  INBOUND  src/adapter/inbound/http/<%= EntityLower %>.ts   (thin Elysia controller, depends on <%= Entity %>Service)
  │     return data( toResponse( await svc.find(id) ) )       toResponse: camel domain → snake wire, Date→ISO
  ▼  SERVICE  src/service/<%= EntityLower %>.ts                 depends on <%= Entity %>Repository
  ▼  OUTBOUND src/adapter/outbound/repository/<%= EntityLower %>.ts   map repo.ErrNotFound → ApiError
<% if (Cache !== 'none') { -%>
  │     CachedRepo.findById:  cache.get ─► <%= Cache %>   (miss) ─► BaseRepo ─► <%= Database === 'drizzle-mysql' ? 'MySQL' : 'Postgres' %>  ─► cache.set (ttl±jitter)
<% } else { -%>
  │     BaseRepo.findById ─► <%= Database === 'drizzle-mysql' ? 'MySQL' : 'Postgres' %>
<% } -%>
  ▼  controller returns { status:true, data:{…} }  ─► Elysia serializes to JSON
  ▼  serverPlugin.onAfterResponse   log: http.method, url.path, status, duration_ms, request_id
  │
HTTP  200  {"status":true,"data":{"id":"…","<%= Fields[0] ? Fields[0].JSONName : 'field' %>":"…","created_at":"…"}}   + x-request-id

errors:  throw new ApiError(...)  ─► serverPlugin.onError  ─► {"status":false,"error_code":"…"} @ its status
         NOT_FOUND→404 · VALIDATION→422 · invalid cursor→400 · everything else→500 (+stack log)
```
<% } else if (Type === 'consumer') { %>
```
<%= Broker %> message  (topic "<%= EntityLower %>s", group "<%= Name %>")
  │
  ▼  consumer.subscribe → src/adapter/inbound/subscriber/handler.ts
  │     decode JSON payload (snake wire) → <%= Entity %>Input
  ▼  SERVICE  src/service/<%= EntityLower %>.ts            depends on <%= Entity %>Repository
<% if (Database !== 'none') { -%>
  ▼  OUTBOUND repository<% if (Cache !== 'none') { %> (CachedRepo + <%= Cache %>)<% } %> ─► <%= Database === 'drizzle-mysql' ? 'MySQL' : 'Postgres' %>
<% } -%>
  ▼  handler resolves ─► ACK        (handler throws ─► NACK / requeue)
       in-flight handlers run to completion during shutdown (context.WithoutCancel analogue)
```
<% } else { %>
```
business event  →  <%= Entity %>Publisher.publish<%= Entity %>(topic, entity)
  │     to<%= Entity %>Event(entity): camel domain → snake wire (Date → ISO)
  ▼  pubsub.Publisher.publish(topic, { key: id, payload })  ─► <%= Broker %>   (at-least-once)
```
<% } %>
